OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779372669
OL,3,CMilitary camp temporarily housing
OL,4,Casylum seekers 'could stay open until
OL,5,C2030'
OL,7,FA military camp temporarily housing
OL,8,Fasylum seekers could stay open until
OL,9,F2030, a "dismayed" local council has
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FWealden District Council said it had
OL,13,Fseen court papers showing Crowborough
OL,14,FTraining Camp in East Sussex will have
OL,15,Fthe option to remain open well beyond
OL,16,Fthe 12 months originally planned.
OL,26,@qD@IOUqD@RO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
