FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779372669
OL,3,CMilitary camp temporarily housing
OL,4,Casylum seekers 'could stay open until
OL,5,C2030'
OL,7,FThe site could accommodate up to 500
OL,8,Fadult male migrants while their claims
OL,9,Ffor asylum in the UK are being
OL,10,Fprocessed, the first of whom moved in
OL,11,Fat the start of the year.
OL,13,FThe council said it was disappointed
OL,14,Fby the Government's "failure to
OL,15,Fcommunicate openly".
OL,17,FThe camp was handed over to the Home
OL,18,FOffice by the Ministry of Defence for
OL,19,Fa year, while longer-term
OL,20,Faccommodation options are found.
OL,26,@vD@UOUwD@SO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779372669
OL,3,CMilitary camp temporarily housing
OL,4,Casylum seekers 'could stay open until
OL,5,C2030'
OL,7,FBorder security and asylum minister
OL,8,FAlex Norris previously told MPs the
OL,9,Fuse of the site would be "temporary".
OL,11,FThe council said in a statement:
OL,12,F"Wealden has been asking the Home
OL,13,FOffice formally about this for some
OL,14,Ftime.
OL,16,F"Pressed finally to answer, the Home
OL,17,FOffice said no decision has been made.
OL,26,@qD@ZOUqD@dO]tD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779372669
OL,3,CMilitary camp temporarily housing
OL,4,Casylum seekers 'could stay open until
OL,5,C2030'
OL,7,F"Once again, Wealden District
OL,8,FCouncil's council leaders are deeply
OL,9,Fdismayed and disappointed by the
OL,10,Fgovernment and Home Office Minister in
OL,11,Ftheir failure to communicate openly
OL,12,Fkey information about the use of
OL,13,FCrowborough Army Camp as temporary
OL,14,Fasylum seeker accommodation."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@]O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
