OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779372669
OL,3,CMilitary camp temporarily housing
OL,4,Casylum seekers 'could stay open until
OL,5,C2030'
OL,7,FThe Government has vowed to end the
OL,8,Fuse of hotels to house asylum seekers
OL,9,Fby the end of this Parliament and
OL,10,Fannounced plans to use the Crowborough
OL,11,Fbase and Cameron Barracks in
OL,12,FInverness, Scotland as part of these
OL,13,Fefforts last year.
OL,15,FThere have been a series of protests
OL,16,Fin Crowborough and a legal challenge
OL,17,Ffrom a local residents group over the
OL,18,Fscheme.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779372669
OL,3,CMilitary camp temporarily housing
OL,4,Casylum seekers 'could stay open until
OL,5,C2030'
OL,7,FThe camp was used to accommodate
OL,8,FAfghan families evacuated during the
OL,9,Fwithdrawal from Kabul in 2021 while
OL,10,Fthey were resettled elsewhere.Council
OL,11,Fleader Rachel Millward, who is also
OL,12,Fdeputy leader of the Green Party,
OL,13,Fsaid: "Everyone round here is wearily
OL,14,Ffamiliar with the Home Office's
OL,15,Finability to make a decision.
OL,26,@uD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779372669
OL,3,CMilitary camp temporarily housing
OL,4,Casylum seekers 'could stay open until
OL,5,C2030'
OL,7,F"People whose lives are directly
OL,8,Faffected by that are left guessing.
OL,9,FWhy can't the minister have the
OL,10,Fcourage to tell it how it is and
OL,11,Foutline a plan, instead of hidden
OL,12,Fconversations behind closed doors?
OL,14,F"The entire project has been
OL,15,Fdisastrously handled by the Home
OL,16,FOffice with a shocking lack of
OL,17,Fcommunication. We struggle to
OL,18,Funderstand how the Home Office can
OL,19,Fjustify such poor mismanagement.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779372669
OL,3,CMilitary camp temporarily housing
OL,4,Casylum seekers 'could stay open until
OL,5,C2030'
OL,7,F"Asylum seekers deserve to be treated
OL,8,Fwith dignity and humanity, not left in
OL,9,Funsuitable temporary accommodation
OL,10,Fwith inadequate support and no
OL,11,Ftransparency for either residents or
OL,12,Fthe local community.
OL,14,F"We have asked the Minister Alex
OL,15,FNorris for an urgent explanation."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUwD@bO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779372669
OL,3,CMilitary camp temporarily housing
OL,4,Casylum seekers 'could stay open until
OL,5,C2030'
OL,7,FA Home Office spokesperson said: "We
OL,8,Fwill continue to do whatever it takes
OL,9,Fto fix the broken asylum system we
OL,10,Finherited by removing the incentives
OL,11,Fdrawing illegal migrants to the UK and
OL,12,Fincreasing removals of those with no
OL,13,Fright to be here.
OL,15,F"We will close all asylum hotels by
OL,16,Fthe end of this Parliament and are
OL,17,Fmoving asylum seekers into more
OL,18,Fsuitable accommodation.
OL,20,F"No decision has been made to extend
OL,21,Fthe use of the Crowborough site."
OL,26,@oD@bOUwD@AOU|D@AOU}D@aO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
